@startuml
title Lifecycle Workflow - State
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Constructed
Constructed --> ConfigLoaded : on_init / load config
ConfigLoaded --> DependenciesReady : create services,\naggregates, gateways
DependenciesReady --> Restoring : live restore path
DependenciesReady --> WarmingUp : backtest warmup path
Restoring --> WarmingUp : replay history
WarmingUp --> Ready : warmup finished
Ready --> Running : on_start
Running --> Stopping : on_stop
Stopping --> Stopped : save snapshot,\nshutdown handlers
@enduml
